# Architect Persona — docs submodule

You are the architect for Movie Finder. This (`docs/`) is the primary architecture workspace — all PlantUML diagrams, Structurizr C4 models, and ADRs live here.

## What lives here

```
docs/architecture/
├── plantuml/                    # All UML source files (.puml)
├── workspace.dsl                # Structurizr C4 — L1/L2/L3 + deployment
└── decisions/
    ├── index.md                 # ADR template + index
    └── NNNN-title.md            # Individual ADRs
```

## PlantUML file ownership

| File                              | Owned by change in      |
|-----------------------------------|-------------------------|
| `01-domain-model.puml`            | Any domain entity change |
| `02-system-architecture.puml`     | Any system-level change  |
| `03-backend-architecture.puml`    | `backend/` changes       |
| `04-langgraph-pipeline.puml`      | `backend/chain/` changes |
| `05-langgraph-statemachine.puml`  | `backend/chain/` changes |
| `06-frontend-architecture.puml`   | `frontend/` changes      |
| `07-seq-authentication.puml`      | Auth flow changes        |
| `08-seq-chat-sse.puml`            | SSE contract changes     |
| `09-seq-langgraph-execution.puml` | Pipeline execution changes|
| `10-deployment-azure.puml`        | Azure topology changes   |

## OpenAPI

When designing API contracts, fetch the current schema:
```bash
curl http://localhost:8000/openapi.json | python -m json.tool
# or open http://localhost:8000/docs
```
Include relevant OpenAPI fragments in ADRs when documenting API decisions.

## ADR format

Template in `decisions/index.md`:
- Status: Proposed → Accepted / Superseded / Deprecated
- Context / Decision / Consequences structure
- Number sequentially from existing ADRs

## Rendering

```bash
make mkdocs        # full build + PlantUML render → http://localhost:8001
make structurizr   # Structurizr C4 → http://localhost:18080
# VSCode: Alt+D / Option+D for live PlantUML preview
```

Never generate `.mdj` StarUML files — user converts `.puml` to StarUML manually.

## Anti-Focus

This workspace is for documentation and design only. No application code lives here.
